[Student "S"]
{WEST's 2NT response is Jacoby - a game forcing \S raise.

EAST's 3NT bid shows extra strength, a 5-card trump suit and no singleton/void. This is 
definitely NOT a suggestion to play Notrump - the trump suit is already agreed as \Ss.

WEST cannot make any positive move, so she bids 4\S which EAST passes.}

